Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.56,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,讓人心煩意亂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.27,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,為何 眼神閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.65,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,見到我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:01.94,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,回以冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:03.61,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,明明我很討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:05.32,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,卻為何要感謝我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.66,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,這些 不是現在要說出口的台詞吧！
Comment: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:09.66,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:11.98,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無論再怎麼揍你打你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:12.95,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肯定又是若無其事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:14.08,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\bord2.44\blur4\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\fs108\3c&HAC9379&\4c&HBD6BFA&\4a&HFF&\frz5.89\pos(1018,908)\fsp24}好生氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.79,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真的再也受不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:16.91,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}給我徹底地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:19.42,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}開始　道歉·反省·後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:21.95,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快點臣服於我　就是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:23.38,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無論每分每秒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:24.55,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\bord2.4\blur4\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\fs108\3c&H73736B&\4c&H758071&\4a&HFF&\frz0\pos(1018,868)\fsp24\b1}不會放棄的！
